      "content": "It's not just being overwhelmed. It's that there's no point anymore. I've lived my life, I've seen everything, and now I'm just a burden to my kids and a ghost in this house. Everything feels so heavy, and I honestly feel like I'm just taking up space that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
